Bangun. Kamu telat.

11
00:00:47,560 --> 00:00:49,399
Da Young, cepat bangun.

12
00:00:49,399 --> 00:00:51,969
Kamu akan telat.

13
00:00:55,340 --> 00:00:56,340
Kamu sudah bangun?

14
00:00:56,969 --> 00:00:59,679
Aduh. Kepalaku sakit.

15
00:00:59,679 --> 00:01:02,810
Sudah pasti. Kamu mabuk berat.

16
00:01:02,810 --> 00:01:04,550
Hei, bangunlah. Kamu bisa telat.

17
00:01:04,749 --> 00:01:07,079
Pukul berapa ini?

18
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:10,449
Sudah pukul 8.00?

19
